OL,3,CFive people arrested in connection
OL,4,Cwith murder probe after death of man,
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FFive people have been arrested in
OL,8,Fconnection with a murder investigation
OL,9,Fin Poole in Dorset.
OL,11,FPolice were called to Longfleet Road
OL,12,Fat 2:13am yesterday (Friday 19 June)
OL,13,Fwhere an 18-year-old man was found
OL,14,Finjured.
OL,16,FHe was taken into hospital for
OL,17,Ftreatment, but died a short time later.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
