CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781953373
OL,3,CFive people arrested in connection
OL,4,Cwith murder probe after death of man,
OL,5,C18
OL,7,FAll five remain in police custody.
OL,9,FDetective Superintendent Neil Third,
OL,10,Fof Dorset Police, said: "We have
OL,11,Finformed the victim's family of these
OL,12,Flatest developments and our thoughts
OL,13,Fare with them at this incredibly
OL,14,Fdifficult time.
OL,16,F"We do not underestimate the concern
OL,17,Fand upset that an incident of this
OL,18,Fnature will have in the community.
OL,26,@rD@YOUxD@AOU
