OL,3,CFive people arrested in connection
OL,4,Cwith murder probe after death of man,
OL,5,C18
OL,7,F"We would like to reassure that we
OL,8,Fhave acted quickly in making arrests
OL,9,Fand progressing our investigation.
OL,11,F"We still need help from the public
OL,12,Fand would reiterate our appeal for
OL,13,Fanyone with information ` or relevant
OL,14,Fhome CCTV, doorbell camera or dashcam
OL,15,Ffootage ` from Dale Close or Longfleet
OL,16,FRoad around the relevant time to
OL,17,Fplease come forward.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
