OL,5,C18
OL,7,F"We are grateful for everyone's
OL,8,Fsupport while the cordon is in place
OL,9,Fand officers are conducting their
OL,10,Fenquiries, it allows us to carry out a
OL,11,Fdetailed investigation and seek
OL,12,Fjustice for the victim's family."
